Well there is some magnesium there, but it wouldn't catch first.  The
metal has to get really hot first by some other sort of fire.  To light an
engine case on fire, you have to put it on top of a bonfire!

An '80 should have an aluminum block IIRC, but the transmission might be
magnesium.

